1. ctrl + N 可以快速查找类
2. ctrl + space可以提示
3. Alt + F7可以查找这个类或者变量、方法在整个项目中出现的位置
4. Alt + Q可以查找类和方法的文档说明
5. ctrl + 左键可以定位到声明
6. Alt + F12，可以定位到当前编辑的文件，然后选定按enter
7. 对变量、方法、类（以下简称三种类型）更改名字，只需要在声明或者任何一个使用的地方，Alt + F6就可以了
8. Alt + o重写积累的方法
9. Alt + i重写接口的方法
10. Alt + Shift + Space可以智能提示
11. Shift+click关掉一个tab，什么意思，试一试
12.  Alt+Insert (Code | Generate) 可以产生getter和setter方法
13. Alt+F1在三种类型的作用？
14. The F12 key moves the focus from the editor to the last focused tool window
15. The Escape key in any tool window moves the focus to the editor.
16. Shift+Escape moves the focus to the editor and also hides the current (or last active) tool window.
17. Ctrl+Alt+T 自动产生try catch块
18. Ctrl+Shift+Space 用于实例化一个类的new关键字后面自动补全
19. Ctrl+Alt+B查看一个抽象方法的实现
20. You can comment or uncomment lines and blocks of code using Ctrl+Slash and Ctrl+Shift+Slash.
21.  Ctrl+Shift+Space 强制类型转换
22. Ctrl+D 复制一行或者一个块（需要自己修改一下这个快捷键）
23. Tab：in a method and press the Tab key to see what happens.Use the Tab key to move between the template fields.
24. Ctrl+Space 可以给你推荐一个变量名
25.  Ctrl+P： 可以提示在一个方法的括号中可以填入那些合法的值
26. Ctrl+Shift+Backspace 回到你上次编辑的地方，Pressing Ctrl+Shift+Backspace a few times moves you deeper into your changes history.
27. Use Ctrl+Shift+F7 (Edit | Find | Highlight Usages in File) to quickly highlight usages of some variable in the current file.
	Use F3 and Shift+F3 keys to navigate through highlighted usages.
	Press Escape to remove highlighting.
28. Use Code | Reformat Code to reformat code according to your code style preferences (File | Settings | Code Style).
	You can also use Code | Optimize Imports to automatically optimize imports (remove unused imports, etc.). To access the corresponding settings, use File | Settings | Code Style | Imports.
	
29.To see your local history of changes in a file, invoke Local History | Show History from the context menu. You can navigate through different file versions, see the differences and roll back to any previous version.
